im.r_c.android.fusioncache

Class LruCacheWrapper<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • im.r_c.android.fusioncache.LruCacheWrapper<K,V>

  • class LruCacheWrapper<K,V>
extends java.lang.Object
    FusionCache Created by richard on 6/13/16.

    A wrapper class of ExtendedLruCache which is a subclass of LruCache, providing a little more features than LruCache.

    This class is NOT thread-safe.

      • get

        public final V get(K key)
        Returns the value for key if it exists in the cache or can be created by #create. If a value was returned, it is moved to the head of the queue. This returns null if a value is not cached and cannot be created.
